The Department of Civil Engineering at the University of Petra organizes a scientific visit to the East Jerash Water Purification Plant : 08-08-2019 11 : 41 : 06 Complete : 1265 eye-systems the Department of Civil Engineering at the University of Petra , a scientific visit to the East Jerash Water Technology Plant with the goal of finishing the Department of Civil Engineering on the machinery for wastewater treatment and the modern techniques used in it .